data.description: HIGHLY MOTIVATED SELLERS!!! DON'T MISS THIS WEST SIDE 3 bedroom HOME of Evansville, Floors are in need of replacing- seller is offering a $5000 allowance. Walking up to this beautiful home you are welcomed with an adorable property charm. This is an amazing home that has modern updates along with aged character providing original woodwork and a fireplace.  On the main floor is the master bedroom that includes ample space for a KING size bed and a second bedroom.  As well on the main floor is a spacious living room, stunning eat in Kitchen, a modernized bathroom, and huge laundry room with a lot of shelving.  Every ROOM IS LARGE!!   Once you make your way up the stairs you will reach another huge bedroom that also includes attic space for a lot of storage, or could even be turned into another room to the house.     An Added benefit outside the home is 1.5 car garage with doggie door. You will love the curb appeal and fenced in yard also privacy with well maintained shrubs. There is plenty of parking with off street and alleyway driveway, Sellers are providing a 1 year home warranty.    DO NOT PASS THIS ONE UP!  Updates and included: Roof 2014, A/C unit 2019, Furnace a new coil-runs great, water heater 2010.  Appliance: Washer/Dryer 2020, Range-electric glass top 2023, Dishwasher 2017
